    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Also at 11th level, you use your power over the soul to craft the perfect henchmen.</p><p> You learn the Shadow Clone Technique.</p><p> This jutsu may use your Charisma as its casting modifier.</p><p> However, you may substitute the cost of each Clone with Humanity.</p><p> Clones summoned using Humanity gain temporary hit points equal to your level + your Proficiency Bonus, can cast an additional jutsu, and add your Charisma modifier to damage it deals.</p><p></p>",
